    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Yes, this should probably align when `others` is a Series. It'll require some care to get right, since it's an API breaking change.\r\n\r\nI'd favor a keyword like `align` for controlling it. For now it'll be `None` by default and if `others` is a series it will not align, but warn that the default will change in the future to align."
